''Multimode 5GHz (802.11a) Wireless Router with 4 Ports''
[ftp://ftp.dlink.com/Gateway/di754/Manual/ Files on '''D-Link''''s USA FTP Server] The [[D-Link DWL-650+ rev A1]] module is '''not included by default'''. "GL5254RT-2A1-B10 VER:T2.0" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The CPU is assumed to be a VR4131. Default settings (including SSIDs) are per '''D-Link''''s manual. :Dimensions, per the manual, are (LxWxH) [[Dimensions::9.25" x 6.25" x 1.5"]]. The power adapter shown in the FCC photos is a '''High Power''' HPW-2005U A2 (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 2.0A MAX -> 5VDC, 3 A).
